                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Article 25</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research" calendar="gregorian"
                        notAfter="1946-10-15T23:59:59+01:00" notBefore="1946-07-29T00:00:00+01:00"
                        >undated</date>
                </dateline>
                <p>Czechoslovakia’s interests are not covered either by the proposal of the Soviet
                    Union or by that of U.S.A., the U.K. and France. The Czechoslovak delegation
                    will present its point of view during the discussion on art. 25.</p>
